<div class="brick-wall" style="opacity:0.5"></div>

<div class="fill center" style="flex-direction:column;gap:22px;z-index:5;padding:30px">
    <div class="neon-sign-stack sm">
        <div class="neon-tommys">Tommy's</div>
        <div class="neon-club">CLUB</div>
    </div>

    <div class="status-icon">&#x23F3;</div>

    <div class="status-heading amber">&#x23F3; REVIEW QUEUE</div>

    <div class="status-body">
        Your email is verified and your access is active.
    </div>
    <div class="status-body-sub">
        Membership review can happen in the background.<br>
        An admin may approve or reject your membership later.
    </div>

    <a href="/auth/refresh-status" class="gate-btn ghost">&#x25B8; Refresh Status</a>

    <p class="status-foot">
        Logged in as <span style="color:var(--neon-cyan)">{{session.user.username}}</span>
        &middot; <form method="POST" action="/logout" style="display:inline"><input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}"><button type="submit" style="background:none;border:0;padding:0;color:var(--neon-cyan);cursor:pointer;font:inherit">sign out</button></form>
    </p>
</div>
